SCORE - View your character stats
==================================

Usage: score

Displays comprehensive information about your character:
  - Name and Level
  - HP (current/max)
  - All stats (STR, DEX, AGI, CON, INT, WIS, CHA)
  - Experience points
  - Gold
  - Currently equipped weapon and armor

This is your main reference for character information.

See also: help stats, help hp
